## 1. Current State

### Existing GotchiScene Buttons
The GotchiScene currently has 6 action buttons and 1 navigation button:

| Button | Current Behavior |
|--------|-----------------|
| Wash | Shows "Wash was clicked" message on screen |
| Groom | Shows "Groom was clicked" message on screen |
| Feed | Shows "Feed was clicked" message on screen |
| Pet | Shows "Pet was clicked" message on screen |
| Play | Shows "Play was clicked" message on screen |
| Give a Break | Shows "Give a Break was clicked" message on screen |
| DETAILED VITALS | Navigates to gotchi_stats scene |

### Gotchi Interaction Methods (declared in `Gotchi.hpp`; bodies UNVERIFIED)
> The following effects are **inferred from the prior plan**, not confirmed against `Gotchi.cpp`.
> Run `grep -n "addStat\|setStat" Gotchi.cpp` and paste the literal output before relying on these.

| Method | Claimed Effects (verify) |
|--------|--------------------------|
| `interact()` | +15 Happiness, +20 Excitement, +1 Friendship, "play" action (2s) |
| `feed()` | Hunger down, +10 Energy, +10 Satisfaction, "eat" action (3s) |
| `play()` | +25 Excitement, +20 Happiness, +1 Agility, "play" action (4s) |
| `clean()` | Cleanliness -> 100, +10 Satisfaction, "idle" action (1s) |
| `heal()` | Health -> 100, +5 Happiness, "idle" action (1s) |
| `sleep()` | Sets sleeping state, "sleep" action |
| `wake()` | Clears sleeping state, +10 Happiness overlay |

