## 2. Verified Stat Reference

These are the **exact enum identifiers and ranges** confirmed in `GotchiStats.cpp`. Use these
spellings verbatim in handler code.

### Emotional stats (`EmotionalStat`, all 0-100 %)
| Identifier | Display name | Default | Note |
|-----------|--------------|---------|------|
| `HAPPINESS` | Happiness | 80 | |
| `EXCITEMENT` | Excitement | 30 | |
| `SATISFACTION` | Satisfaction | 60 | |
| `LOVE` | Love | 50 | description is literally "Affection" |
| `FRIEDNSHIP` | Friendship | 0 | **MISSPELLED IN ENUM — must type `FRIEDNSHIP`** |
| `JOY` | Joy | 70 | |

### Secondary stats (`SecondaryStat`) — the ONLY public path to the core vitals
| Identifier | Display name | Default | Range | Semantics |
|-----------|--------------|---------|-------|-----------|
| `FITALITY` | Health | 100 | 0-100 | alias of core HEALTH |
| `FOOD_LEVEL` | Hunger | 0 | 0-100 | **0 = full, 100 = starving** (feeding lowers it) |
| `HYDRATION` | Thirst | 0 | 0-100 | 0 = hydrated, 100 = dehydrated |
| `ENERGY` | Energy | 100 | 0-100 | alias of core ENERGY |
| `SLEEP_DEBT` | Sleep | 0 | 0-100 | 0 = rested, 100 = exhausted |
| `CLEANLINESS` | Hygiene | 100 | 0-100 | alias of core HYGIENE |

### Physical stats (`PhysicalStat`, 0-100 %)
| Identifier | Default |
|-----------|---------|
| `AGILITY` | 50 |

### Social stats (`SocialStat`)
| Identifier | Default | Unit | Note |
|-----------|---------|------|------|
| `FRIENDS` | 0 | `#` (count) | reserve for real social encounters, NOT touch-bonding |

