|--------|--------|
| Removed moods `FUNNY`, `RESTED`, `CLEAR` | Not present in `GotchiMoodType`; would not compile |
| Play mood -> `MOOD_31_PLAYFUL`; Break -> `MOOD_13_CALM`/`MOOD_12_RELIEVED` | Valid replacements |
