| Documented core-vs-alias duplication risk (4.3) | Silent desync risk on Hunger/Energy/Hygiene/Health |
| Added "reserved for hex board" stat list (4.2) | Keeps screen-button footprint small, per scope |
| Marked base-method effects UNVERIFIED (1) | `Gotchi.cpp` not available at plan time |

